commitResults.messageTitle: Rename chatbot and add greeting messages

commitResults.messageBody: chatbot echoes user's messages until user types 'bye'

commitResults.messageTitle: Implement Add and List feature for chatbot
commitResults.messageBody:
Add ability to store whatever text is entered by user, and display them
back when requested.
Add the ability to mark tasks as done, as well as unmarking tasks.

commitResults.messageTitle: Modify code to follow coding standard

commitResults.messageBody:
- Consolidate commands ("list", "mark" and "unmark") using a switch
statement.
- Move repeated code into helper methods to improve clarity.

-Create these new classes so that the chatbot supports tracking of these
tasks
-Implemented toString method among all classes, allowing these classes to override the toString method in their parent class, Task.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add handling of invalid user inputs - Handle missing description for Todo by displaying an error message - Handle invalid command from user by displaying an error message
Refactor code and Add exception handling for Mark and Unmark commands
commitResults.messageBody:
- Extract printing of divider into a method for easier usage
- Add exception handling for mark/unmark commands ensure that the task
  number given by user is a number and is within the list of tasks.
  Otherwise, display an error message to user.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Exception handling for Deadline and refactor code
commitResults.messageBody:
- Extract code for retrieving task description and task deadline

- getDescription and getDeadline in Deadline.java handles missing or invalid inputs
